data.description: Amazing Home! 4 bedroom 3 full bathroom home in the Ola School District with a bedroom and full bath on main level, perfect for guests or older kids! No Carpet on the main level! Spacious owners suite has trey ceiling & walk in closet. Owner's bath has his & her sinks, garden tub and separate shower. All bath rooms have tile floors. Nice level and fenced backyard, ideal for kids, pets or privacy! Warm and inviting neighborhood with sidewalks, pool and friendly neighbors! Super convenient to new Publix shopping center,
